WEBVTT

00:10.314 --> 00:13.100
Narrator: AT THIS VERY MOMENT
IN THE TOWN OF COEUR D'COEURS,

00:13.143 --> 00:16.625
A GIRL NAMED CHUCK WAS ATTENDING
HER FATHER'S FUNERAL.

00:16.668 --> 00:18.540
THE ONLY PARENT
SHE HAD EVER KNOWN

00:18.583 --> 00:21.412
WAS ACCIDENTALLY,
INADVERTENTLY KILLED

00:21.456 --> 00:23.153
BY THE BOY SHE LOVED,

00:23.197 --> 00:25.155
WHO WAS,
AT THIS VERY MOMENT,

00:25.199 --> 00:27.505
ATTENDING
HIS OWN MOTHER'S FUNERAL,

00:27.549 --> 00:30.595
WHO HAD ACTUALLY DIED TWICE.

00:30.639 --> 00:33.033
IT WAS A BLOOD VESSEL BURSTING
IN HER BRAIN

00:33.076 --> 00:36.645
THAT CAUSED NED'S MOTHER'S
FIRST DEATH.

00:36.688 --> 00:40.214
HOWEVER,
YOUNG NED HAD A SECRET GIFT.

00:40.257 --> 00:43.869
HE COULD TOUCH DEAD THINGS
AND BRING THEM BACK TO LIFE.

00:43.913 --> 00:46.394
I MUST'VE SLIPPED.
CLUMSY.

00:46.437 --> 00:48.222
DID THE TIMER GO OFF?

00:48.265 --> 00:51.225
IT WAS A GIFT
WITH TWO SIMPLE CAVEATS --

00:51.268 --> 00:54.445
KEEP A DEAD THING ALIVE
FOR MORE THAN A MINUTE,

00:54.489 --> 00:58.014
AND SOMETHING ELSE
WOULD DIE IN ITS PLACE.

01:02.845 --> 01:06.414
AND TOUCH A DEAD THING TWICE,
IT DIES AGAIN --

01:06.457 --> 01:09.025
THIS TIME...FOREVER.

01:09.069 --> 01:10.766
[ THUD ]

01:10.809 --> 01:15.205
YOUNG NED FELT RESPONSIBLE,
NOT ONLY FOR HIS MOTHER'S DEATH,

01:15.249 --> 01:17.947
BUT THE DEATH OF CHUCK'S FATHER.

01:17.990 --> 01:21.081
HIS FEELINGS OF GUILT
WERE AMPLIFIED

01:21.124 --> 01:24.736
BECAUSE HE, TOO, WAS IN LOVE.

01:24.780 --> 01:27.783
THE NEXT TIME YOUNG NED
WOULD SEE THE GIRL NAMED CHUCK,

01:29.611 --> 01:32.135
SHE WOULD BE DEAD.

01:32.179 --> 01:35.617
UNLIKE CHUCK,
YOUNG NED STILL HAD A FATHER.

01:35.660 --> 01:37.619
BUT AFTER
A BRIEF MOURNING PERIOD,

01:37.662 --> 01:39.011
HE WOULD DEPOSIT NED

01:39.055 --> 01:42.276
AT THE LONGBOROUGH SCHOOL
FOR BOYS.

01:42.319 --> 01:44.104
AFTER HER OWN FATHER'S DEATH,

01:44.147 --> 01:47.455
CHUCK WAS FOSTERED
BY AUNTS LILY AND VIVIAN,

01:47.498 --> 01:49.892
A RENOWNED
SYNCHRONIZED SWIMMING DUO

01:49.935 --> 01:51.546
AND SISTER NEUROTICS

01:51.589 --> 01:56.028
WHO HELPED HER BUILD A NEW HOME
BEE BY BEE.

01:56.072 --> 01:57.769
IT WAS AUNT LILY

01:57.813 --> 02:00.424
WHO FOUND THE AD ON THE BACK
PAGES OF THE THRIFTY NICKEL

02:00.468 --> 02:03.862
IN A FLEETING WISP OF SOMETHING
RESEMBLING MATERNAL INSTINCT.

02:03.906 --> 02:05.516
I JUST WANTED YOU
TO STOP STARING

02:05.560 --> 02:07.518
AT THAT SPOT
WHERE YOUR FATHER DIED.

02:07.562 --> 02:11.087
YOUNG CHUCK REBUILT HER HOME
BY BUILDING A NEW HOME

02:11.131 --> 02:13.655
FOR A HOMELESS QUEEN
AND HER HIVE.

02:13.698 --> 02:16.658
THE BEES THRIVED.
SO DID CHUCK.

02:16.701 --> 02:18.399
AND WHILE CHUCK THRIVED,

02:18.442 --> 02:21.924
NED WAITED FOR HIS FATHER
TO BRING HIM HOME.

02:21.967 --> 02:23.621
AND WAITED.

02:23.665 --> 02:25.493
AND WAITED.

02:25.536 --> 02:28.844
JUST AS CHUCK REMEMBERED
HOW HOME FELT,

02:28.887 --> 02:33.196
NED TRIED NOT TO FORGET
WHAT HOME WAS.

02:33.240 --> 02:36.156
HE HELD ON TO IT
THE ONLY WAY HE COULD...

02:38.245 --> 02:40.986
...AND BECAME THE PIE MAKER.

02:44.076 --> 02:47.471
AND THE GIRL NAMED CHUCK
BECAME DEAD.

02:47.515 --> 02:49.821
SHE WAS 28 YEARS, 24 WEEKS,

02:49.865 --> 02:52.607
3 DAYS, 11 HOURS,
AND 51 MINUTES OLD

02:52.650 --> 02:56.219
WHEN MURDERED
ON A TAHITIAN GETAWAY.

02:56.263 --> 02:57.786
BUT ONE TOUCH
FROM THE PIE MAKER...

02:57.829 --> 03:00.919
HEY, I THINK SOMEBODY'S TRUCK'S
ON FIRE.

03:00.963 --> 03:02.312
OH, GEEZ!

03:02.356 --> 03:05.620
Narrator:
...AND SHE WAS ALIVE ONCE MORE.

03:05.663 --> 03:07.230
SORRY I'M LATE.

03:07.274 --> 03:09.885
Narrator: THE PIE MAKER
COULD NEVER TOUCH HER AGAIN.

03:09.928 --> 03:13.584
CHUCK'S SURVIVAL NOW DEPENDED
ON A DELICATE DANCE,

03:13.628 --> 03:15.238
A BALLET OF AVOIDANCE.

03:15.282 --> 03:16.283
Chuck: GOING.

03:16.326 --> 03:17.501
STOPPING.

03:17.545 --> 03:18.763
-CROSSING.
-WAITING.

03:18.807 --> 03:19.982
Narrator: THE PIE MAKER
TOOK PRECAUTIONS

03:20.025 --> 03:22.463
TO ENSURE CHUCK FELT SAFE
AT HOME.

03:22.506 --> 03:25.640
SLIPPERS WERE WORN
ADORNED WITH BELLS.

03:25.683 --> 03:27.076
-GOING.
-STOPPING.

03:27.119 --> 03:28.904
FOLLOWING.

03:28.947 --> 03:31.733
Narrator: DIGBY KEPT HIS EYES
OPEN TO THE HAZARDS OF TOUCH,

03:31.776 --> 03:36.216
A CANINE PROXIMITY ALERT
WHO COULD NOT ONLY PLAY DEAD...
[ DIGBY BARKS ]

03:36.259 --> 03:37.695
[ HORN BLARES ]

03:37.739 --> 03:41.003
...BUT COULD DO SO
FROM EXPERIENCE.

03:41.046 --> 03:42.657
[ BARKS ]
OH! OH!

03:42.700 --> 03:45.007
Narrator: NEITHER THE PIE MAKER
NOR CHUCK COULD MOVE

03:45.050 --> 03:47.923
WITHOUT THE OTHER ONE KNOWING.

03:47.966 --> 03:52.667
AND TO THE PIE MAKER,
IT FELT LIKE HOME.

03:52.710 --> 03:56.018
SO, CHUCK AND THE PIE MAKER
BUILT A HOME TOGETHER

03:56.061 --> 03:58.150
BEE BY BEE.

03:58.194 --> 04:01.589
TRAGICALLY, ROGUE PESTICIDES
KILLED THOSE BEES,

04:01.632 --> 04:03.155
BUT ONLY BRIEFLY.

04:03.199 --> 04:05.201
THIS WILL GO BETTER
IF YOU WEAR LESS CLOTHES.

04:05.245 --> 04:07.943
OKAY, YOU'VE ALREADY GOT ME
SHUCKED LIKE AN EAR OF CORN.

04:07.986 --> 04:09.249
WELL, I'M SHUCKED, TOO,

04:09.292 --> 04:11.120
ALL THE WAY DOWN
TO MY SILKY INTIMATES

04:11.163 --> 04:13.078
JUST TO PUT ON
A BEEKEEPER'S SUIT.

04:13.122 --> 04:15.820
REMIND ME
WHY YOU'RE SHUCKED AND SILKY.

04:15.864 --> 04:17.213
I THOUGHT
IT WAS ONLY FAIR.

04:17.257 --> 04:20.216
[ CHUCKLES ]

04:20.260 --> 04:21.609
YOU STOPPED BEING FAIR.

04:21.652 --> 04:22.914
RIGHT.

04:22.958 --> 04:24.786
YOU DO REALIZE
I CAN GET NEW BEES.

04:24.829 --> 04:26.918
I CAN MAKE A NEW HOME
FOR NEW BEES.

04:26.962 --> 04:28.311
YOU LOVE THESE BEES.

04:28.355 --> 04:29.965
A HAPPY HIVE'S A HAPPY HOME,

04:30.008 --> 04:32.489
AND YOU CAN'T BE HAPPY
IF YOU'RE DEAD.

04:32.533 --> 04:34.796
THERE ARE
1,000 DEAD BEES HERE.

04:34.839 --> 04:36.058
[ SIGHS ]

04:36.101 --> 04:37.451
I DON'T WANT
1,000 BUTTERFLIES TO DIE

04:37.494 --> 04:38.974
BECAUSE YOU BRING MY BEES
BACK TO LIFE.

04:39.017 --> 04:41.455
THINK ABOUT IT
AS A PEST-CONTROL ISSUE.

04:41.498 --> 04:44.284
THERE'S A WATER BUG INFESTATION
IN THE DRAINPIPES.

04:44.327 --> 04:46.503
IF I TOUCH 1,000
LITTLE DEAD BEES TO LIFE

04:46.547 --> 04:49.550
MAYBE 1,000 LITTLE WATER BUGS
WILL NO LONGER BE A PROBLEM.

04:49.593 --> 04:51.508
OH, LAST TIME I ASKED YOU
TO BRING SOMETHING BACK TO LIFE,

04:51.552 --> 04:52.770
YOU SAID NO.

04:52.814 --> 04:54.468
IT WAS YOUR DAD.

04:54.511 --> 04:56.513
THAT WOULD HAVE BEEN WEIRD,
IF NOT ACTIVELY TRAUMATIC.

04:56.557 --> 04:58.298
HMM.

04:58.341 --> 05:00.125
TO BRING MY DAD BACK, EVEN
FOR A MINUTE, MAY BE GHOULISH,

05:00.169 --> 05:02.214
BUT IT'S ALSO SWEET.

05:02.258 --> 05:03.999
IT'S LIKE
A TAXIDERMIED PET

05:04.042 --> 05:06.044
OR STUFFING SOMEONE'S ASHES
IN A TEDDY BEAR.

05:06.088 --> 05:08.264
IF YOU COULD BRING YOUR DAD
BACK JUST FOR A MINUTE,

05:08.308 --> 05:09.483
YOU'RE SAYING YOU WOULDN'T?

05:09.526 --> 05:11.049
THAT WOULD BE
AN AWKWARD MINUTE.

05:11.093 --> 05:13.008
I HAVEN'T SEEN OR HEARD
FROM THE MAN IN 20 YEARS.

05:13.051 --> 05:17.142
I'LL STICK TO BEES.
AT LEAST THEY KNOW WHAT HOME IS.

05:17.186 --> 05:19.188
THIS IS
VERY, VERY SWEET OF YOU.

05:19.231 --> 05:21.146
AND WILL PROBABLY STING.

05:21.190 --> 05:23.105
WELL,
DON'T OFFEND THE BEES.

05:25.412 --> 05:32.070
HOW WOULD I OFFEND
THE BEES?

05:32.114 --> 05:35.030
[ BEES BUZZING ]

05:36.814 --> 05:39.730
[ BARKING ]

05:52.743 --> 05:56.921
Narrator:
OLIVE SNOOK ONCE FELT AS AT HOME
IN HER PIE HOLE UNIFORM

05:56.965 --> 05:58.793
AS SHE DID HER OWN SKIN.

05:58.836 --> 06:03.145
BUT RECENTLY, HOME AND UNIFORM
HAD BEGUN TO CHAFE.

06:03.188 --> 06:05.582
BELIEVING CHUCK
MERELY FAKED HER DEATH,

06:05.626 --> 06:09.064
OLIVE KEPT THE SECRET
THAT CHUCK WAS STILL ALIVE.

06:09.107 --> 06:11.153
BUT THE SECRET
THAT WEIGHED THE MOST

06:11.196 --> 06:13.068
IN OLIVE'S SATCHEL OF DECEPTION

06:13.111 --> 06:16.506
WAS THAT SHE WAS STILL IN LOVE
WITH THE PIE MAKER.

06:18.203 --> 06:21.685
AT THAT VERY MOMENT,
PRIVATE INVESTIGATOR EMERSON COD

06:21.729 --> 06:25.733
WAS ENJOYING A NEW LOVE
OF THE POP-UP VARIETY.

06:25.776 --> 06:27.299
COMBINING HIS FONDNESS

06:27.343 --> 06:29.867
OF DETECTIVE WORK
AND STRESS KNITTING,

06:29.911 --> 06:33.871
MR. COD AUTHORED AND CONSTRUCTED
"LIL' GUM SHOE."

06:33.915 --> 06:35.482
I LOVE YOU, LIL' GUM SHOE.

06:35.525 --> 06:38.136
Narrator: MR. COD HAD TIME
TO AUTHOR POP-UPS

06:38.180 --> 06:40.443
BECAUSE HE SAVED TIME
SOLVING MURDERS

06:40.487 --> 06:42.924
WITH A PIE MAKER
WHO CAN UNDEAD THE DEAD

06:42.967 --> 06:45.492
AND ASK HOW THEY GOT THAT WAY.

06:45.535 --> 06:47.319
MY WIFE
HAS BEEN MURDERED!

06:47.363 --> 06:49.452
WELL, WHAT THE PO-PO GOT TO SAY
ABOUT YOUR WIFE BEING MURDERED?

06:49.496 --> 06:51.628
A WORK-RELATED MISHAP.
SAID SHE WAS SLOPPY.

06:51.672 --> 06:53.151
-WAS SHE SLOPPY?
-SHE WASN'T SLOPPY.

06:53.195 --> 06:54.936
SHE WAS HAVING AN AFFAIR.

06:54.979 --> 06:57.417
SAID SHE WAS GONNA LEAVE ME
OR HIM -- I'M NOT SURE WHICH.

06:57.460 --> 06:59.027
SHE WASN'T USING
PROPER NOUNS,

06:59.070 --> 07:00.463
BUT THANK GOD
I WAS EAVESDROPPING.

07:00.507 --> 07:02.117
IF YOUR OLD LADY
WAS STEPPING OUT ON YOU,

07:02.160 --> 07:03.814
WHY YOU GIVE A DAMN
WHO KILLED HER?

07:03.858 --> 07:06.295
I WAS HOPING SHE WAS GONNA
LEAVE HIM AND NOT ME.

07:06.338 --> 07:08.079
I COULDN'T BEAR IT
IF SHE LEFT ME.

07:08.123 --> 07:09.167
UH-HUH.

07:09.211 --> 07:10.560
WHAT LINE OF WORK SHE IN?

07:10.604 --> 07:12.649
BEES. DO YOU KNOW
ANYTHING ABOUT BEES?

07:12.693 --> 07:15.696
I KNOW SOMEBODY WHO --
WHO KNOWS SOMEBODY.

07:15.739 --> 07:17.567
[ SIGHS ]

07:17.611 --> 07:21.658
WELL, UH, LET ME JUST SAY
THAT I'M SORRY ABOUT YOUR LOSS.

07:21.702 --> 07:25.270
AND I DO ACCEPT
CREDIT CARDS.

07:25.314 --> 07:27.577
Narrator:
THE FACTS WERE THESE --

07:27.621 --> 07:30.319
ONE KENTUCKY FITZ,
WIFE OF DUSTY,

07:30.362 --> 07:34.584
WAS THE NUMBER-ONE BEE-GIRL
OF BETTY'S BEES.

07:34.628 --> 07:36.673
BETTY'S BEES -- TRADEMARK --

07:36.717 --> 07:39.328
WAS ALL THE BUZZ IN BEAUTY
AND WELL-BEING

07:39.371 --> 07:42.026
WITH HONEY
AND HONEY-BASED MOISTURIZERS,

07:42.070 --> 07:45.377
ANTI-AGING CREAMS, SOAPS,
AND LIP BALMS.

07:45.421 --> 07:50.818
KENTUCKY WAS 26 YEARS, 3 WEEKS,
5 DAYS, AND 39 MINUTES OLD

07:50.861 --> 07:52.733
WHEN FOUND STUNG TO DEATH

07:52.776 --> 07:56.301
BEHIND THE WHEEL
OF HER BETTY'S BEES BEE-MOBILE.

07:56.345 --> 07:57.738
WHICH ONE
IS KENTUCKY FITZ?

07:57.781 --> 07:59.566
BISCUITS.
BISCUITS?

07:59.609 --> 08:02.351
YOU GOT BISCUITS,
YOU GOT SHRIMPS.

08:02.394 --> 08:04.962
BISCUITS.
SHRIMPS.

08:05.006 --> 08:06.964
YOU GOT SOMETHING WE COULD USE
TO FLIP HER OVER?

08:07.008 --> 08:08.488
WHY YOU GOT
TO FLIP HER OVER?

08:08.531 --> 08:10.185
FRONT DON'T LOOK NO DIFFERENT
THAN THE BACK.

08:10.228 --> 08:12.579
IT AIN'T LIKE YOU GONNA BE
HAVING A CONVERSATION.

08:12.622 --> 08:14.537
IT SURE AIN'T.

08:20.369 --> 08:23.285
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

08:23.328 --> 08:25.243
[ WATCH TICKING ]

08:25.287 --> 08:26.418
OHH.

08:26.462 --> 08:28.551
KENTUCKY?

08:28.595 --> 08:30.988
MAYBE SHE'S PARALYZED
FROM ALL THE BEE STINGS.

08:31.032 --> 08:32.816
I'M JUST TAKING IN
MY SURROUNDINGS.

08:32.860 --> 08:34.775
APPARENTLY, I'M DEAD.

08:34.818 --> 08:36.777
-EEE.
-OOH.

08:36.820 --> 08:38.343
REALLY?

08:38.387 --> 08:41.085
OH, I'M SORRY,
BUT WAS YOUR DEATH ACCIDENTAL?

08:41.129 --> 08:43.697
WAS I ACCIDENTALLY SWARMED
BY BEES? NO.

08:43.740 --> 08:45.699
I MAY HAVE BEEN UP
TO SOME MISCHIEF.

08:45.742 --> 08:47.527
YOUR HUSBAND THINKS
WHAT GOT YOU KILLED

08:47.570 --> 08:49.833
WAS SOME WORKPLACE ROMANCE
GOING ALL SORTS OF SOUR.

08:49.877 --> 08:52.053
AND MY HUSBAND HAS A PROBLEM
WITH EAVESDROPPING.

08:52.096 --> 08:53.837
THERE WAS NO ROMANCE.

08:53.881 --> 08:57.101
IT WAS MY WORKPLACE WENT SOUR.
I WAS LEAVING BETTY'S BEES.

08:57.145 --> 08:59.364
DID YOU TELL DUSTY
YOU WERE LEAVING BETTY'S BEES?

08:59.408 --> 09:01.018
IF I TOLD HIM
I WAS QUITTING,

09:01.062 --> 09:02.759
HE WOULD WORRY
AND ASK A LOT OF QUESTIONS,

09:02.803 --> 09:05.240
AND THEN I'D HAVE TO LIE
ABOUT SABOTAGING BETTY'S BEES.

09:05.283 --> 09:07.372
WHY DID YOU SABOTAGE
BETTY'S BEES?

09:07.416 --> 09:09.984
WHY?
BECAUSE BETTY HAD IT COMING.

09:10.027 --> 09:12.726
INTENTION WAS TO QUIT
BEFORE I GOT CAUGHT.

09:12.769 --> 09:14.162
WHO CAUGHT YOU?

09:14.205 --> 09:16.512
I COULDN'T SEE HIS FACE
OR HER FACE.

09:16.556 --> 09:19.863
ALL THE LIGHTS WENT OUT
ONE BY ONE.

09:19.907 --> 09:22.953
AND THEN THERE WAS
A TERRIBLE HUM.

09:22.997 --> 09:26.783
THEN OUT OF THE DARKNESS,
IT CAME FOR ME.

09:26.827 --> 09:28.524
IT SPIT SOMETHING,

09:28.568 --> 09:31.005
AND THEN A SWARM OF BEES
ATTACKED.

09:31.048 --> 09:33.094
I TRIED TO GET
A GOOD LOOK AT IT,

09:33.137 --> 09:36.314
BUT THE BEES WERE ALREADY
STINGING MY EYES.

09:36.358 --> 09:39.100
THAT'S TERRIFYING.

09:39.143 --> 09:41.842
THAT'S TERRIFYING!

09:41.885 --> 09:43.191
OH, SORRY.
5 SECONDS!

09:43.234 --> 09:44.322
HOW'D YOU SABOTAGE
BETTY'S BEES?

09:44.366 --> 09:45.715
DO YOU HAVE
ANY LAST WISHES?

09:45.759 --> 09:47.282
MY ONLY WISH
IS THAT DUSTY NOT BE ALONE.

09:47.325 --> 09:49.414
YEAH, YEAH.
HOW'D YOU SABOTAGE BETTY'S BEES?

09:49.458 --> 09:53.375
WITH A LOT OF MIGHT.

09:53.418 --> 09:54.724
THAT'S NICE.

09:54.768 --> 09:56.639
WE DON'T KNOW
WHAT SHE WAS DOING,

09:56.683 --> 09:59.337
BUT WE DO KNOW
IT TOOK A LOT OF EFFORT.

09:59.381 --> 10:01.992
DO YOU HEAR SOMETHING?

10:02.036 --> 10:03.298
[ HUMMING ]

10:03.341 --> 10:04.386
IS SHE STILL BREATHING?!

10:04.429 --> 10:05.648
THAT'S NOT BREATHING.

10:05.692 --> 10:09.130
[ BEES BUZZING ]

10:09.173 --> 10:10.697
AAH!
OHH!

10:12.829 --> 10:14.222
[ DOOR SLAMS ]

10:14.265 --> 10:16.180
I TOLD YOU
NOT TO TURN HER OVER.

10:20.532 --> 10:22.099
COULD THAT HAVE HAPPENED TO ME
ON THE ROOF?

10:22.143 --> 10:23.623
COULD I HAVE BEEN SWARMED?
IN MY UNDERWEAR, TOO.

10:23.666 --> 10:25.450
I COULD HAVE BEEN SWARMED
IN MY UNDERWEAR.

10:25.494 --> 10:27.104
Emerson: HEY!

10:27.148 --> 10:28.715
YOU DON'T JUST GET TO PUT
THEM PICTURES IN MY HEAD.

10:28.758 --> 10:30.281
THAT'S AN ASSAULT
ON MY IMAGINATION.

10:30.325 --> 10:31.979
POOR KENTUCKY.
WHAT A HORRIBLE WAY TO DIE --

10:32.022 --> 10:34.024
THOUSANDS OF LITTLE STINGERS
STINGING YOU.

10:34.068 --> 10:36.418
LIKE LITTLE STINGING SECRETS
THAT DON'T JUST STING YOU ONCE.

10:36.461 --> 10:39.726
THEY KEEP STINGING YOU UNTIL
YOU'RE BLOATED AND FULL OF PUS.

10:39.769 --> 10:41.684
WHO WANTED A LA MODE?
AH.

10:41.728 --> 10:44.339
Ned: WELL, KENTUCKY
WAS BLOATED AND FULL OF PUS

10:44.382 --> 10:46.428
BECAUSE SHE WAS SABOTAGING
BETTY'S BEES.

10:46.471 --> 10:47.908
BOY, KENTUCKY SURE HAD IT IN
FOR BETTY,

10:47.951 --> 10:49.823
BUT WHO HAD IT IN
FOR KENTUCKY?

10:49.866 --> 10:51.825
THE TERRIFYING BEEMAN.

10:51.868 --> 10:53.696
WHAT IF HE WAS MADE
ENTIRELY OUT OF BEES,

10:53.740 --> 10:55.132
AND THAT'S WHY
SHE COULDN'T SEE HIS FACE,

10:55.176 --> 10:56.656
BECAUSE HE DIDN'T EVEN
HAVE ONE?

10:56.699 --> 10:58.658
I MEAN, WHAT IF THERE'S
A WHOLE BEEFOLK SOCIETY

10:58.701 --> 11:00.616
WHO WALK AROUND
SHAPED LIKE PEOPLE?

11:00.660 --> 11:02.313
YOU'RE THINKING ABOUT
HOW YOU CAN TRAIN YOUR BEES

11:02.357 --> 11:03.967
TO WALK AROUND IN PEOPLE SHAPES,
AREN'T YOU?

11:04.011 --> 11:05.577
YEAH.

11:05.621 --> 11:07.623
AIN'T NO BEES WALKING AROUND
IN NO PEOPLE SHAPES.

11:07.667 --> 11:09.190
KENTUCKY WAS
WIGGETY-WIGGETY-WHACKED.

11:09.233 --> 11:11.409
WITH A SWARM OF BEES.

11:11.453 --> 11:13.281
SMELLS LIKE
AN INSIDE JOB.

11:13.324 --> 11:15.326
KENTUCKY WAS TALKING
TO SOMEONE AT BETTY'S BEES

11:15.370 --> 11:16.806
WHEN DUSTY
WAS DROPPING EAVES.

11:16.850 --> 11:18.373
SOMEONE WHO KNEW
WHAT SHE WAS DOING

11:18.416 --> 11:19.635
AND WHO WOULD WANT
TO KILL HER FOR IT.

11:19.679 --> 11:20.680
HMM.

11:20.723 --> 11:21.898
WELL, IF IT IS AN INSIDE JOB,

11:21.942 --> 11:24.205
WE'RE GONNA NEED
AN INSIDE BEE-GIRL.

11:24.248 --> 11:25.685
NO.

11:25.728 --> 11:27.469
WE GOT TO TAP THIS HONEY
AT THE SOURCE.

11:27.512 --> 11:29.036
UH-HUH.

11:29.079 --> 11:32.169
HA HA.
"CALLING ALL BEE-GIRLS!"

11:35.695 --> 11:38.741
Narrator:
UNDER THE NOM DE PLUME
OF KATHERINE "KITTY" PIMMS,

11:38.785 --> 11:42.397
CHUCK ANSWERED THE CALL
CALLING FOR BEE-GIRLS.

11:42.440 --> 11:45.748
YOU KNOW, I FIND THAT
THE MOST AMAZING CREATURES

11:45.792 --> 11:47.358
HAVE FURRY BEHINDS.

11:47.402 --> 11:49.447
Narrator: SITTING
IN WOOLSEY NICHOLLS' OFFICE,

11:49.491 --> 11:52.146
DISCUSSING
THE FURRY BEHINDS OF BEES,

11:52.189 --> 11:56.977
CHUCK REALIZED THIS WAS HER
VERY FIRST JOB INTERVIEW EVER.

11:57.020 --> 12:00.197
SHE CONSIDERED THIS FACT
FOR A MOMENT, THEN HAD TO ASK...

12:00.241 --> 12:01.938
I HAVE TO ASK.

12:01.982 --> 12:04.332
ARE YOU THE WOOLSEY NICHOLLS
FROM BZZZZZZZZZ! HONEY AND MORE?

12:04.375 --> 12:06.726
MM.
YES, I AM.

12:06.769 --> 12:08.075
WELL, WHY ARE YOU HERE?

12:08.118 --> 12:09.511
ISN'T BETTY'S BEES
YOUR BIGGEST RIVAL?

12:09.554 --> 12:11.034
I OWN BETTY'S BEES NOW.

12:11.078 --> 12:12.993
WE MADE THE ACQUISITION
VERY QUIETLY.

12:13.036 --> 12:16.474
THESE DAYS, MERGER CAN SEND
BRAND LOYALISTS INTO A TIZZY.

12:16.518 --> 12:19.390
WELL, I'M A HONEY LOYALIST,
AND YOU'LL GET NO TIZZY FROM ME.

12:19.434 --> 12:21.479
I JUST HOPE
YOU'RE NOT KILLING BEE-GIRLS.

12:21.523 --> 12:23.090
I BEG YOUR PARDON?

12:23.133 --> 12:24.613
THE BEE-GIRLS SALES DIVISION.

12:24.656 --> 12:26.093
I MEAN,
WITH ANY ACQUISITION,

12:26.136 --> 12:28.312
THERE'S ALWAYS DOWNSIZING
AND RESTRUCTURING.

12:28.356 --> 12:30.401
I JUST HOPE IT DOESN'T AFFECT
THE BEE-GIRLS.

12:30.445 --> 12:33.317
THE BEE-GIRLS WILL ALWAYS
HAVE A HOME IN MY HIVE.

12:33.361 --> 12:37.017
UNFORTUNATELY,
ALTHOUGH FORTUNATE FOR YOU,

12:37.060 --> 12:39.933
WE'VE RECENTLY HAD AN OPENING
IN THE BEE-GIRL DIVISION.

12:39.976 --> 12:42.065
OH, YEAH, I HEARD ABOUT THAT.
KENTUCKY FITZ --

12:42.109 --> 12:44.807
SOMETHING ABOUT
A HONEY-HARVESTING TRAGEDY?

12:44.851 --> 12:47.810
YES.
IT'S VERY SAD.

12:47.854 --> 12:50.421
SHE HAD A VERY BRIGHT FUTURE
HERE AT THE NEW BETTY'S BEES.

12:50.465 --> 12:51.814
YEAH.

12:51.858 --> 12:53.250
I ALSO HEARD
THAT SHE WAS THINKING OF,

12:53.294 --> 12:55.687
UM, LEAVING BETTY'S BEES
BEFORE SHE DIED.

12:55.731 --> 12:57.211
UH-HUH, UH-HUH, UH-HUH.

12:57.254 --> 12:58.734
WELL, YOU SURE HEAR
A LOT OF THINGS.

12:58.778 --> 13:00.823
VERY GOSSIPY OFFICE.
YES.

13:00.867 --> 13:03.130
WELL, I THINK YOU WILL FIND
THAT PARTICULAR RUMOR

13:03.173 --> 13:04.305
TO BE FALSE,

13:04.348 --> 13:06.786
BECAUSE KENTUCKY
WAS INVESTED.

13:06.829 --> 13:09.136
SHE WAS THE NEW FACE
OF BETTY'S BEES.

13:09.179 --> 13:12.226
WE DESIGNED OUR ENTIRE
BRAND RELAUNCH AROUND HER.

13:12.269 --> 13:14.402
BUT BETTY IS THE FACE
OF BETTY'S BEES.

13:14.445 --> 13:15.838
OH, NO, NO.

13:15.882 --> 13:18.362
SEE, BETTY --
BETTY'S THE OLD FACE, HUH?

13:18.406 --> 13:20.974
"OLD" BEING
THE OPERATIVE WORLD.

13:21.017 --> 13:22.497
SHE'S 37.

13:22.540 --> 13:24.020
SHE'S 38,
WHICH ROUNDS UP TO 40,

13:24.064 --> 13:26.196
WHICH ROUNDS UP TO 50,
WHICH ROUNDS UP TO OLD.

13:26.240 --> 13:28.764
AND IF YOU WERE
IN THE BUSINESS

13:28.808 --> 13:30.853
OF TRYING TO SELL
A PRODUCT

13:30.897 --> 13:33.160
THAT PROMISES YOUTH,
BEAUTY, AND VITALITY,

13:33.203 --> 13:35.292
YOU HAVE TO MAKE
A STRONG CASE FOR IT.

13:35.336 --> 13:36.903
-MM-HMM.
-CORRECTION.

13:36.946 --> 13:39.035
WE HAVE TO MAKE
A STRONG CASE FOR IT.

13:39.079 --> 13:40.820
KITTY,
I WOULD BE HONORED

13:40.863 --> 13:45.563
IF YOU CALLED BETTY'S BEES
YOUR NEW HOME.

13:45.607 --> 13:47.652
BETTY'S BEES
IS MY NEW HOME.

13:47.696 --> 13:49.785
AH, STUPENDOUS.

13:49.829 --> 13:50.960
[ CHUCKLING ]

13:51.004 --> 13:52.266
WELL...

13:52.309 --> 13:53.876
CHUCK HAS A NEW HOME.
I BLAME YOU.

13:53.920 --> 13:56.052
I BLAME ME, TOO.
THAT WENT WELL.

13:56.096 --> 13:58.098
Narrator:
EMERSON COD'S INSIDE MAN,

13:58.141 --> 14:01.797
A.K.A. BETTY'S BEES'
NEWEST BEE-GIRL KITTY PIMMS,

14:01.841 --> 14:04.887
BUZZED THROUGH THE OFFICES
OF BETTY'S BEES

14:04.931 --> 14:09.892
UNTIL SHE BUZZED UPON THE OFFICE
OF ONE KENTUCKY FITZ.

14:09.936 --> 14:14.854
CHUCK/KITTY SEARCHED FOR
ANY HINT OF A SABOTEUR'S AGENDA.

14:23.166 --> 14:25.821
OH.

14:25.865 --> 14:27.344
Narrator: WHAT SHE FOUND...
AAH!

14:27.388 --> 14:29.346
...WAS THE EPONYMOUS BETTY BEE.

14:29.390 --> 14:30.739
WHAT ARE YOU DOING
IN THERE?

14:30.782 --> 14:32.872
COGNITIVE THERAPY
FOR CLAUSTROPHOBIA.

14:32.915 --> 14:35.135
YOU'RE BETTY BEE.
THAT'S RIGHT.

14:35.178 --> 14:37.267
WHY AM I EXPLAINING MYSELF
TO YOU?

14:37.311 --> 14:39.139
YOU SHOULD BE
EXPLAINING YOURSELF TO ME.

14:39.182 --> 14:40.488
OH, I'M SORRY.

14:40.531 --> 14:41.924
I THOUGHT THIS OFFICE
WAS VACANT.

14:41.968 --> 14:43.926
I'M KITTY PIMMS.
I'VE JUST BEEN HIRED.

14:43.970 --> 14:45.014
BY WHOM?

14:45.058 --> 14:46.537
WOOLSEY NICHOLLS.

14:46.581 --> 14:48.061
WOOLSEY?

14:48.104 --> 14:50.106
SO YOU'RE REPLACING
KENTUCKY?

14:50.150 --> 14:52.935
A LITTLE SOON AFTER HER DEATH
SEEMS DISTASTEFUL,

14:52.979 --> 14:54.502
DON'T YOU THINK?

14:54.545 --> 14:56.156
IT DOES, BUT IT ALSO SPEAKS
TO THE EFFICIENCY

14:56.199 --> 14:58.071
OF YOUR HUMAN RESOURCES
DEPARTMENT.

14:58.114 --> 14:59.681
MM-HMM.

14:59.724 --> 15:02.336
I WONDER HOW ELSE
YOU'LL BE REPLACING KENTUCKY.

15:02.379 --> 15:03.990
SINCE I'M A WITHERED HAG,

15:04.033 --> 15:06.601
TATTERED BY EVERY GRAIN OF SAND
IN THE HOURGLASS,

15:06.644 --> 15:08.951
BETTY'S BEES STILL NEEDS
A FRESH, YOUNG FACE,

15:08.995 --> 15:10.387
AND AFTER WHAT HAPPENED
TO KENTUCKY,

15:10.431 --> 15:11.693
WELL, NO ONE WANTS
TO THINK ABOUT THAT

15:11.736 --> 15:14.565
WHEN THEY'RE BUYING
LIP BALM.

15:14.609 --> 15:16.524
WELCOME TO BETTY'S BEES.

15:19.788 --> 15:24.010
Narrator:
KENTUCKY'S AFFAIRS WERE CLEARLY
A BEE IN BETTY BEE'S BONNET.

15:30.190 --> 15:33.497
OH, I-I JUST WANTED TO SAY
WHAT AN HONOR IT IS

15:33.541 --> 15:34.585
TO BE WORKING WITH YOU.

15:34.629 --> 15:36.196
THANK YOU.
GET OUT.

15:36.239 --> 15:38.676
Narrator:
AND SO CHUCK GOT OUT.

15:38.720 --> 15:40.591
BUT THE QUESTION REMAINED.

15:40.635 --> 15:43.725
BETTY BEE --
COCONSPIRATOR OR KILLER?

15:43.768 --> 15:45.640
KENTUCKY WAS GONNA BE
THE NEW FACE OF BETTY'S BEES,

15:45.683 --> 15:47.729
WHICH DOES
GIVE BETTY MOTIVE.

15:47.772 --> 15:48.904
BEING REPLACED BY YOUNG
AND BETTER-LOOKING

15:48.948 --> 15:50.514
ALWAYS GIVES YOU MOTIVE.

15:50.558 --> 15:53.517
BUT KENTUCKY WAS SABOTAGING
BETTY'S BEES' TRADEMARK,

15:53.561 --> 15:54.910
WHICH WAS OWNED
BY WOOLSEY NICHOLLS,

15:54.954 --> 15:56.346
WHICH GIVES WOOLSEY MOTIVE.

15:56.390 --> 15:57.782
WOOLSEY'S A BUSINESSMAN.

15:57.826 --> 15:59.262
SOMEBODY SABOTAGED HIM,

15:59.306 --> 16:01.786
HE'D SEND IN A SWARM OF LAWYERS,
NOT BEES.

16:01.830 --> 16:03.179
I KNOW.

16:03.223 --> 16:05.747
THEY WERE LOVERS
OF THE SAME-SEX PERSUASION,

16:05.790 --> 16:08.358
AND THE KEY
IS FOR THEIR LOVE NEST.

16:08.402 --> 16:10.491
MM, WE'VE RULED OUT
WORKPLACE ROMANCE.

16:10.534 --> 16:11.883
OH.

16:11.927 --> 16:14.321
I'LL JUST CROSS THAT
OFF MY LIST, THEN.

16:14.364 --> 16:16.801
I HAVEN'T RULED OUT
WORKPLACE ROMANCE.

16:16.845 --> 16:18.673
Emerson: ROMANCE DOES
GIVE YOU MOTIVE.

16:18.716 --> 16:22.024
SOMEBODY ALWAYS LOVING SOMEBODY
THEY SHOULDN'T BE LOVING.

16:24.853 --> 16:28.291
-IS THAT FOR YOUR AUNTS?
-MM-HMM. EXTRA VANILLA.

16:28.335 --> 16:30.990
Narrator: OLIVE SNOOK
DISCOVERED IT WASN'T VANILLA

16:31.033 --> 16:33.601
WHILE DELIVERING PIE
TO CHUCK'S AUNTS.

16:33.644 --> 16:37.344
IT WASN'T THE ONLY SECRET
SHE WOULD DISCOVER THAT NIGHT.

16:37.387 --> 16:39.607
THE HIGH DOSES
OF HERBAL MOOD ENHANCERS

16:39.650 --> 16:42.566
NOT ONLY CAUSED
PARTICULARLY VIVID SIDE EFFECTS,

16:42.610 --> 16:45.047
BUT THEY ALSO PROMPTED
A CONFESSION.

16:45.091 --> 16:47.136
I'M CHARLOTTE'S MOTHER.

16:47.180 --> 16:48.529
Narrator:
IT WAS A CONFESSION

16:48.572 --> 16:50.922
NOT EVEN LILY'S SISTER, VIVIAN,
HAD HEARD,

16:50.966 --> 16:52.924
AND TO ENSURE
THAT SHE NEVER WOULD,

16:52.968 --> 16:55.666
LILY BANISHED OLIVE
FROM THEIR LIVES.

16:55.710 --> 16:58.887
SINCE BOTH CHUCK AND HER MOTHER
WERE SUPPOSED TO BE DEAD,

16:58.930 --> 17:01.020
NEITHER COULD KNOW
THE OTHER WAS ALIVE.

17:01.063 --> 17:02.804
I DON'T KNOW
IF BETTY KILLED KENTUCKY

17:02.847 --> 17:05.024
OR IF SHE DIDN'T KILL KENTUCKY,
BUT I KNOW THIS.

17:05.067 --> 17:07.374
BETTY KNOWS SOMETHING
ABOUT SOMETHING.

17:07.417 --> 17:08.984
ALRIGHT, I'LL GIVE BETTY
THE SHAKEDOWN TOMORROW.

17:09.028 --> 17:10.420
NO. NO SHAKING.

17:10.464 --> 17:11.726
WHAT IF SOMEONE
FROM BETTY'S BEES

17:11.769 --> 17:13.554
FINDS OUT YOU'RE A SPY?

17:13.597 --> 17:15.991
SPYING IS A LOT LIKE SABOTAGE
IN THAT THEY KILL YOU FOR IT.

17:16.035 --> 17:18.602
THAT'S WHAT YOU DO WITH SPIES
AND SABOTEURS -- YOU KILL THEM.

17:18.646 --> 17:21.649
AND YOU DON'T FEEL BAD BECAUSE
THEY'RE SPYING AND SABOTAGING.

17:21.692 --> 17:23.912
NED, THEY'RE NOT GONNA KILL ME
DURING OFFICE HOURS.

17:23.955 --> 17:25.218
YEAH.

17:25.261 --> 17:27.176
STOP TRYING TO SPOOK
MY INSIDE MAN.

17:27.220 --> 17:29.526
YOU COULD DIE.
AND YOU'RE ALREADY DEAD.

17:29.570 --> 17:31.224
TOLD YOU SHE WASN'T DEAD.

17:36.316 --> 17:39.667
IF I COULD BREATHE,
I WOULD VOMIT.

17:39.710 --> 17:41.103
OLIVE SNOOK,

17:41.147 --> 17:42.583
EVERY WEEK
A DELICIOUS LIFE-GIVING PIE,

17:42.626 --> 17:44.193
AND THEN NOTHING
FOR MONTHS.

17:44.237 --> 17:46.674
I THOUGHT YOU WERE DEAD,
AND SO SOON AFTER CHARLOTTE.

17:46.717 --> 17:48.545
I WAS BEGINNING TO TAKE
EVERYONE'S DYING PERSONALLY.

17:48.589 --> 17:49.851
WE WOULD HAVE CALLED,

17:49.894 --> 17:51.374
BUT BY THE TIME I KNEW
WE WERE COMING,

17:51.418 --> 17:52.897
VIVIAN WAS ALREADY
ON THE BUS.

17:52.941 --> 17:54.595
LILY WAS VERY TENACIOUS.

17:54.638 --> 17:57.641
SHE TRIED TO GET ME TO COME HOME
IN SIX CONSECUTIVE STOPS.

17:57.685 --> 17:59.295
SHE INSISTED ON COMING
ALL THIS WAY

17:59.339 --> 18:02.820
JUST TO ASK
WHY YOU STOPPED DELIVERING PIES.

18:02.864 --> 18:05.736
I'M...

18:05.780 --> 18:07.608
...REALLY FLAKY.

18:07.651 --> 18:10.089
THAT'S WHAT I TOLD HER!
IT'S NOT ABOUT THE PIES,

18:10.132 --> 18:12.569
ALTHOUGH THE PIES WERE ALWAYS
LOVELY AND SO VIVID.

18:12.613 --> 18:16.356
I GOT TO GO GET
SOMEBODY'S, UH, SOMETHING.

18:23.972 --> 18:25.756
GET OUTTA HERE.

18:25.800 --> 18:28.846
THEY'RE HERE BECAUSE YOU STOPPED
DELIVERING THEIR SPECIAL PIES.

18:28.890 --> 18:30.718
ALL THIS TIME I'VE BEEN MAKING
SPECIAL PIES, AND WHAT --

18:30.761 --> 18:32.589
AND DOSING THEM
WITH GOD KNOWS WHAT

18:32.633 --> 18:34.504
YOU CLAIM THAT IS VANILLA,
BUT THAT AIN'T VANILLA.

18:34.548 --> 18:35.853
I'M GONNA DOSE
THE BOTH OF Y'ALL

18:35.897 --> 18:37.377
WITH A SCOOP
OF SHUT-THE-FUDGE-UP.

18:37.420 --> 18:39.335
Narrator:
THE WEIGHT OF KEPT SECRETS

18:39.379 --> 18:42.686
HAD BECOME UNBEARABLE
FOR THE PINT-SIZED PIE SLINGER.

18:42.730 --> 18:45.385
WHY WON'T YOU TALK TO ME?
I THOUGHT YOU WERE MY FRIEND.

18:45.428 --> 18:47.082
LIKE I SAID, FLAKY.

18:47.126 --> 18:48.823
I GOT SOMETHING TO SAY.

18:48.866 --> 18:52.522
I'M GONNA SAY IT TO YOU
AND YOU AND YOU AND YOUR HUMP.

18:52.566 --> 18:54.481
Narrator:
OLIVE WANTED TO LET LOOSE

18:54.524 --> 18:57.440
THE SECRETS AND LIES SHE'D BEEN
FORCE-FED BY HER FRIENDS --

18:57.484 --> 19:01.227
THAT CHUCK WAS STILL ALIVE,
THAT LILY WAS HER MOTHER.

19:01.270 --> 19:03.881
BUT INSTEAD
WHAT CAME OUT WAS THIS...

19:03.925 --> 19:08.451
AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAHHH!

19:13.064 --> 19:14.544
[ Squeaking ] AAH.

19:14.588 --> 19:15.980
WHAT'S GOTTEN INTO YOU?

19:16.024 --> 19:18.766
I AM A SAWED-OFF SHOTGUN
FULL OF SECRETS!

19:18.809 --> 19:20.202
DID SHE SAY SHE WAS ARMED?

19:20.246 --> 19:22.117
NO, I DON'T HAVE A GUN.
I AM A GUN.

19:22.161 --> 19:24.163
AT ANY MOMENT,
TRUTH BUCKSHOT

19:24.206 --> 19:26.295
COULD COME SPEWING OUT
OF MY MUZZLE.

19:26.339 --> 19:28.079
-LOOK OUT!
-THAT'S ENOUGH. THAT'S ENOUGH.

19:28.123 --> 19:30.212
TRUER WORDS
WERE NEVER SPOKEN.

19:30.256 --> 19:33.520
THIS RIFLE IS GONNA GO AWAY
IN A LITTLE SATIN-LINED CASE

19:33.563 --> 19:35.696
WITH THE TRIGGER LOCKED
AND THE SAFETY ON.

19:35.739 --> 19:37.045
â™ª I QUIT

19:37.088 --> 19:38.438
I'M QUITTING YOU.

19:38.481 --> 19:42.964
AND -- AND THIS.
AND, YOU KNOW, ALL OF THIS.

19:43.007 --> 19:45.401
OLIVE, YOU DON'T HAVE TO QUIT.
YOU HAVE TO CALM DOWN.

19:45.445 --> 19:47.664
YOU WANT A DRINK?
LILY, HAND ME YOUR PURSE.

19:47.708 --> 19:49.710
I'M NOT THIRSTY.

19:53.931 --> 19:56.151
I'M TENDERING
MY RESIGNATION.

19:56.195 --> 19:58.327
AND RESIGNING MY TENDERS

19:58.371 --> 20:03.419
TO THE COLD, HARSH REALITY
OF WHAT'S NOT MEANT TO BE.

20:04.899 --> 20:06.422
BUT YOU CAN'T JUST LEAVE.

20:09.077 --> 20:10.731
-VIVIAN, GO WAIT OUTSIDE.
-BUT --

20:10.774 --> 20:12.776
HAVEN'T YOU CAUSED
ENOUGH TROUBLE?

20:14.996 --> 20:16.911
THIS IS YOUR HOME.
WHERE WILL YOU...GO?

20:20.044 --> 20:21.655
I KNOW A PLACE.

20:33.797 --> 20:35.234
AUNT VIVIAN
USED TO ALWAYS SAY

20:35.277 --> 20:38.019
THERE'S NOTHING SADDER
THAN AN EMPTY BIRDCAGE.

20:38.062 --> 20:39.542
IS OLIVE
EVER GONNA COME HOME?

20:39.586 --> 20:41.327
SHE DIDN'T SAY --
WOULDN'T SAY.

20:41.370 --> 20:43.111
SHE JUST SAID HER APARTMENT WAS
PAID TILL THE END OF THE YEAR,

20:43.154 --> 20:45.853
AND SHE ASKED ME
TO WATER HER PLANTS.

20:45.896 --> 20:47.942
I FEEL LIKE I BROKE HER.

20:47.985 --> 20:50.466
I ENLISTED HER
TO SPY ON MY AUNTS

20:50.510 --> 20:54.122
AND THEN TURNED HER INTO
A HOMEOPATHIC DRUG MULE.

20:54.165 --> 20:57.081
WHAT KIND OF HOMEOPATHIC DRUGS
WAS SHE MULING?

20:57.125 --> 20:58.735
I BAKED ANTI DEPRESSANTS
INTO THEIR PIES

20:58.779 --> 21:01.260
TO TRY TO GET THEM
OUT OF THE HOUSE.

21:01.303 --> 21:04.654
IT'S SOMETHING I'VE ALWAYS
WANTED TO DO WHEN I WAS ALIVE,
BUT I NEVER HAD THE CHANCE.

21:04.698 --> 21:06.700
I...GUESS IT WORKED?

21:06.743 --> 21:09.746
I GOT THEM OUT OF THE HOUSE.
OLIVE GOT THEM OUT OF THE HOUSE.

21:09.790 --> 21:11.966
THEY GOT OUT OF THE HOUSE.

21:12.009 --> 21:15.012
AUNT VIVIAN TOOK THE BUS.
SHE NEVER TAKES THE BUS.

21:15.056 --> 21:19.016
SHE THINKS
IT'S TOO INTIMATE. HMM.

21:19.060 --> 21:21.367
I WISH THERE WAS A WAY
I COULD THANK OLIVE.

21:21.410 --> 21:23.760
YOU KNOW, TODAY WAS MY FIRST DAY
AT BETTY'S BEES,

21:23.804 --> 21:25.284
AND THAT WAS MY FIRST
JOB INTERVIEW EVER.

21:25.327 --> 21:27.808
I MEAN, I HAVEN'T GONE ANYWHERE
WITH MY LIFE,

21:27.851 --> 21:29.462
AND THIS IS MY SECOND ONE.

21:29.505 --> 21:31.681
ALL I HAVE IS A FAKE RESUME

21:31.725 --> 21:33.640
FILLED WITH THINGS
I'VE NEVER EVEN DONE.

21:33.683 --> 21:35.468
I MEAN,
I'VE NEVER EVEN LIVED ALONE.

21:35.511 --> 21:37.731
[ SIGHS ]
HOW LONG DID YOU LIVE ALONE?

21:37.774 --> 21:38.993
LONG ENOUGH.

21:39.036 --> 21:40.386
DON'T YOU THINK
THAT'S ODD?

21:40.429 --> 21:41.952
I THINK THAT'S REALLY ODD --
MY ENTIRE LIFE.

21:41.996 --> 21:43.737
MY AUNTS SWEPT IN
THE MOMENT MY DAD DIED,

21:43.780 --> 21:45.347
AND THEN YOU SWEPT IN
THE MOMENT I DIED.

21:45.391 --> 21:48.655
YOU'RE THINKING ABOUT
LIVING HERE NOW, AREN'T YOU?

21:48.698 --> 21:50.221
YEAH.

21:50.265 --> 21:52.746
WELL, YOU HATE CORDUROY
AND SLEIGH-BELL SLIPPERS,

21:52.789 --> 21:55.401
AND...I'LL STOP
WALKING IN ON YOU

21:55.444 --> 21:57.490
DOING THINGS YOU DON'T WANT ME
TO KNOW YOU'RE DOING.

21:57.533 --> 21:59.492
THAT WOULD NEVER HAVE
HAPPENED IF YOU WERE
WEARING YOUR SLIPPERS.

21:59.535 --> 22:00.928
IT'LL BE ROMANTIC.

22:00.971 --> 22:02.103
I'M CONFUSED. MORE.

22:02.146 --> 22:03.583
-MORE?
-MORE OF AN EXPLANATION.

22:03.626 --> 22:04.975
HOW IS IT ROMANTIC?

22:05.019 --> 22:06.890
YOU'VE GOT A JOB
AND NOW YOU'RE MOVING OUT?

22:06.934 --> 22:09.110
BUT I DIDN'T GET A JOB.

22:09.153 --> 22:11.373
I'M UNDERCOVER KITTY,
AND I'M NOT MOVING OUT.

22:11.417 --> 22:13.244
I'M JUST MOVING
NEXT DOOR.

22:13.288 --> 22:14.550
I MEAN, IT'S FRENCH.

22:14.594 --> 22:17.074
IT'S VERY FIRST-CLASS
PARISIAN LIVING.

22:17.118 --> 22:18.989
YOU KNOW,
HIS-AND-HERS SUITES

22:19.033 --> 22:20.904
AND COY MIDNIGHT KNOCKS
ON THE DOOR

22:20.948 --> 22:22.341
TO SHARE A LOVER'S BOUDOIR.

22:22.384 --> 22:23.385
YOU'LL BE KNOCKING?

22:23.429 --> 22:25.039
YOU CAN KNOCK, TOO.

22:25.082 --> 22:27.781
Narrator: THIS WAS NOT ROMANTIC
FOR THE PIE MAKER.

22:27.824 --> 22:29.739
YAY. KNOCKING.

22:32.655 --> 22:34.309
WHERE'S OLIVE?

22:34.353 --> 22:38.748
Narrator: OLIVE SNOOK WAS
WHERE LILY HAD TAKEN HER.

22:43.057 --> 22:45.973
[ VOCALIZING, BELL CHIMING ]

22:50.107 --> 22:53.023
[ VOCALIZING CONTINUES ]

23:02.990 --> 23:05.079
-Shh!
-Shh!

23:05.122 --> 23:08.212
Narrator: IT WAS A PLACE
THAT VALUED OLIVE'S SILENCE

23:08.256 --> 23:10.171
AS MUCH AS LILY DID.

23:13.261 --> 23:14.828
HELLO, BETTY!

23:14.871 --> 23:17.439
A LITTLE BEE TELLS ME
YOU'VE MET KITTY PIMMS.

23:17.483 --> 23:18.788
BRIEFLY.

23:18.832 --> 23:20.224
WELL, THIS MORNING
KITTY SAYS TO ME,

23:20.268 --> 23:22.357
SHE SAYS, "I WANT TO SPEAK
TO BETTY BEE.

23:22.401 --> 23:24.968
BEE-GIRL TO BEE-GIRL, TELL HER
HOW MUCH SHE MEANS TO ME."

23:25.012 --> 23:26.100
BLESS.

23:26.143 --> 23:27.667
UH, OH!

23:27.710 --> 23:30.234
AND, UH, IF THERE'S A LULL
IN THE CONVERSATION,

23:30.278 --> 23:32.367
YOU JUST ASK KITTY
WHY SHE LOVES BEES.

23:32.411 --> 23:34.804
HUH? OH.
YOU'LL BE GLAD YOU DID.

23:34.848 --> 23:36.327
THANK YOU.
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

23:36.371 --> 23:37.894
BETTY, LOOK.

23:37.938 --> 23:39.374
I KNOW KENTUCKY WAS
YOUR NUMBER-ONE BEE-GIRL,

23:39.418 --> 23:40.636
AND I'M NOT LOOKING
TO REPLACE HER.

23:40.680 --> 23:42.333
I JUST WANT TO LIVE UP
TO HER STANDARD

23:42.377 --> 23:44.335
OF HONEY HARVESTING
AND SALES EXCELLENCE.

23:44.379 --> 23:45.815
YOU'RE NOT REALLY
GOING TO STAND THERE

23:45.859 --> 23:47.600
AND KISS MY ASS,
ARE YOU?

23:47.643 --> 23:49.340
OR DIDN'T WOOLSEY TELL YOU?

23:49.384 --> 23:50.516
HE DIDN'T.

23:50.559 --> 23:51.560
HOW POLITIC.

23:51.604 --> 23:53.040
TELL ME WHAT?

23:53.083 --> 23:54.998
WOOLSEY'S ACQUISITION
WAS A HOSTILE TAKEOVER.

23:55.042 --> 23:57.131
NO, HE DIDN'T MENTION
THE HOSTILE PART.

23:57.174 --> 23:59.133
OH, YES. THE ASS
YOU WERE JUST KISSING

23:59.176 --> 24:02.136
IS NOW JUST THE ASS
OF A RETIRED HONEY MASCOT.

24:02.179 --> 24:05.531
THAT'S MY NEW TITLE --
HONEY MASCOT/CONSULTANT.

24:05.574 --> 24:07.750
IT USED TO BE FOUNDER
AND PRESIDENT.

24:07.794 --> 24:11.188
THAT WOULD MAKE ME
STINGING MAD.

24:11.232 --> 24:14.453
EH, I GET TO KEEP MY OLD OFFICE,
JUST NOT MY DIGNITY.

24:14.496 --> 24:16.193
WHEN ALL OF YOUR BEES DIE,

24:16.237 --> 24:18.326
IT'S HARD TO CARE
ABOUT ANY OF IT.

24:18.369 --> 24:20.067
ALL YOUR BEES DIED?

24:20.110 --> 24:22.809
THE COLONY COLLAPSED.
MITES MIGHT HAVE CAUSED IT.

24:22.852 --> 24:24.114
IN FACT, WE KNOW THEY DID.

24:24.158 --> 24:25.551
TOOK OVER EVERY HIVE

24:25.594 --> 24:27.857
NOT LONG AFTER WOOLSEY
TOOK OVER BETTY'S BEES.

24:27.901 --> 24:32.166
MIGHT ALMOST BE POETIC IF...
IT DIDN'T SUCK SO MUCH.

24:32.209 --> 24:35.082
Narrator: KENTUCKY DIDN'T
SABOTAGE BETTY'S BEES

24:35.125 --> 24:36.562
WITH A LOT OF MIGHT.

24:36.605 --> 24:38.651
SHE SABOTAGED
BETTY'S BEES WITH...

24:38.694 --> 24:41.131
A LOT OF MITES.

24:41.175 --> 24:44.047
IT WOULD TAKE A LOT OF MITES
TO CAUSE A COLONY COLLAPSE.

24:44.091 --> 24:45.614
SURE DOES.

24:45.658 --> 24:49.009
I GREW UP WITH GENERATIONS
OF THOSE BEES.

24:49.052 --> 24:52.882
THE FIRST HIVE
WAS AN INFESTATION

24:52.926 --> 24:55.319
IN THE CORNER OF MY BEDROOM.

24:55.363 --> 24:57.626
I WAS 5.

24:57.670 --> 24:59.280
I TRIED TO KILL IT.

24:59.323 --> 25:00.542
OH.

25:00.586 --> 25:02.326
I WAS STOPPED.

25:02.370 --> 25:04.851
MOTHER WAS A METHODIST, AND
DADDY WAS A PRAGMATIST, SO...

25:04.894 --> 25:08.245
GOD PUT THOSE BEES THERE
FOR A REASON.

25:08.289 --> 25:09.682
THEY WERE RIGHT.

25:09.725 --> 25:13.250
YOU LIVED WITH BEES?
THAT SOUNDS MAGICAL.

25:13.294 --> 25:16.732
WE CALLED IT
THE HONEY HOUSE.

25:16.776 --> 25:18.647
THE HONEY HOUSE
IS EMPTY NOW.

25:18.691 --> 25:21.737
WE LEFT TOGETHER,
ME AND THE BEES.

25:21.781 --> 25:24.566
THOSE BEES
BUILT BETTY'S BEES.

25:24.610 --> 25:28.135
WHAT HAPPENED TO THOSE BEES?
COULD IT BE SABOTAGE?

25:28.178 --> 25:30.267
A CONSPIRACY?

25:30.311 --> 25:31.791
HOW DRAMATIC.

25:31.834 --> 25:34.968
YOU THINK SOMEONE
INTENTIONALLY MURDERED MY BEES.

25:35.011 --> 25:36.186
JUST A THOUGHT.

25:36.230 --> 25:38.580
IT WASN'T SABOTAGE, KITTY.

25:38.624 --> 25:41.670
SOMETIMES BAD THINGS
JUST HAPPEN.

25:41.714 --> 25:45.718
Narrator: UNBEKNOWNST TO CHUCK,
A.K.A. KITTY PIMMS,

25:45.761 --> 25:50.331
SOMETHING BAD WAS ABOUT TO
"JUST HAPPEN" TO HER.

25:55.249 --> 25:56.555
DID KENTUCKY TALK ABOUT
COLONY COLLAPSE?

25:56.598 --> 25:58.295
IS IT UPSETTING?

25:58.339 --> 26:00.210
SHE TENDS NOT TO TELL ME THINGS
IF THEY MIGHT BE UPSETTING.

26:00.254 --> 26:02.299
IT'S WHEN A BEEHIVE
BECOMES INHOSPITABLE --

26:02.343 --> 26:04.127
IN THIS CASE,
INFESTED WITH MITES.

26:04.171 --> 26:05.433
THEN ALL THE BEES
FLY AWAY TO DIE.

26:05.476 --> 26:07.261
IT'S A NATURAL PHENOMENON.

26:07.304 --> 26:09.655
EXCEPT WHEN A BEE COMPANY GETS
BOUGHT OUT BY ITS CHIEF RIVAL

26:09.698 --> 26:11.395
AND ITS STAR EMPLOYEE DEAD,

26:11.439 --> 26:13.528
THEN MAYBE IT DON'T HAPPEN
SO NATURALLY.

26:13.572 --> 26:17.097
SEE, KENTUCKY --
SHE WAS SABOTAGING BETTY'S BEES,

26:17.140 --> 26:19.360
WHICH TOOK A LOT OF MIGHT,
AS IN EFFORT,

26:19.403 --> 26:20.883
AND A LOT OF MITES,
AS IN PESTS.

26:20.927 --> 26:22.493
SHE WAS INFECTING
THE HIVES.

26:22.537 --> 26:24.670
SOMEBODY FOUND OUT,
AND THEY KILLED HER FOR IT.

26:24.713 --> 26:26.715
HOW DO YOU KNOW
SHE WAS SABOTAGING ANYTHING?

26:26.759 --> 26:28.151
SHE CONFESSED.

26:28.195 --> 26:29.588
BEFORE SHE DIED.

26:29.631 --> 26:32.503
B-- NOT TO US,
BUT TO A RELIABLE SOURCE,

26:32.547 --> 26:34.244
WHO WISHES
TO REMAIN ANONYMOUS.

26:34.288 --> 26:36.464
IS YOUR RELIABLE SOURCE
BETTY BEE?

26:36.507 --> 26:38.248
WHAT MAKES YOU SAY THAT?

26:38.292 --> 26:40.729
KENTUCKY WAS VERY CLOSE WITH
BETTY. THEY WERE LIKE SISTERS

26:40.773 --> 26:42.688
UNTIL SOMEONE ASKED KENTUCKY
TO BE THE NEW BETTY.

26:42.731 --> 26:44.907
Chuck: LOOK, I KNOW IT MUST BE
VERY HARD TO LEARN

26:44.951 --> 26:46.517
THAT YOUR WIFE WAS KILLED
BECAUSE OF SABOTAGE,

26:46.561 --> 26:48.650
BUT AT LEAST
SHE WASN'T CHEATING ON YOU.

26:48.694 --> 26:51.305
SHE LOVED YOU VERY, VERY MUCH,
AND SHE'D NEVER HURT YOU.

26:51.348 --> 26:53.307
SHE WAS THE ONLY FAMILY
I EVER HAD --

26:53.350 --> 26:57.311
YOU KNOW THAT I LIKED
AND LIKED ME.

26:57.354 --> 26:59.400
IF I WAS MORE COMFORTABLE
WITH YOU PEOPLE, I'D CRY.

26:59.443 --> 27:01.750
-OH, YOU CAN CRY. IT'S OKAY.
-THANKS.

27:01.794 --> 27:05.536
IT IS NOT OKAY FOR A
GROWN-ASS MAN TO WEEP IN PUBLIC

27:05.580 --> 27:07.582
WITH A BUNCH OF HAPPY FAMILIES
ENJOYING PIE.

27:10.803 --> 27:12.674
IF YOU CAN'T HOLD IT,

27:12.718 --> 27:14.937
YOU TAKE YOUR ASS
TO THE MEN'S ROOM

27:14.981 --> 27:17.766
AND CRY IN PRIVATE
ON THE TOILET...

27:17.810 --> 27:19.072
LIKE A MAN!

27:19.115 --> 27:20.900
-I NEED TO USE THE MEN'S ROOM.
-OH.

27:20.943 --> 27:23.511
LOOK, I KNOW WHERE BETTY
PUT THE KEY.

27:23.554 --> 27:24.947
I CAN GET IT TOMORROW.

27:24.991 --> 27:26.645
SHE'S NOT GONNA STAY
IN HER OFFICE ALL DAY.

27:26.688 --> 27:28.429
HMM.

27:29.604 --> 27:31.171
WHAT?

27:31.214 --> 27:32.607
I THOUGHT YOU WAS
GONNA START SQUAWKING

27:32.651 --> 27:34.478
ABOUT HOW DANGEROUS
IT'D BE TO GO BACK.

27:34.522 --> 27:36.263
SQUAWK, SQUAWK.
[ CHUCKLES ]

27:36.306 --> 27:38.047
I'M NOT GONNA WAG MY FINGER
IF THAT'S WHAT YOU EXPECT.

27:38.091 --> 27:40.397
IT'S CHUCK'S LIFE, AND SHE CAN
LIVE IT HOWEVER SHE'D LIKE.

27:40.441 --> 27:41.964
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

27:42.008 --> 27:44.184
I CAN'T EXPECT HER TO SIT
INSIDE ALL DAY AND...

27:44.227 --> 27:45.359
HIDE!

27:45.402 --> 27:46.403
NO, I DON'T NEED TO --

27:46.447 --> 27:48.014
WOMAN, HIDE YOUR ASS!

27:50.669 --> 27:53.236
OH, VIVIAN.
I DIDN'T KNOW YOU WERE HERE.

27:53.280 --> 27:56.239
UM, WE'RE JUST CLOSING UP.

27:56.283 --> 27:58.502
THERE.
ALL CLOSED.

27:58.546 --> 28:00.287
THERE'S STILL PEOPLE
INSIDE.

28:00.330 --> 28:02.071
CLEANING CREW.
HOW ARE YOU?

28:02.115 --> 28:04.987
TO BE HONEST, I WASN'T CRAVING
PIE, I WAS CRAVING COMPANY.

28:05.031 --> 28:06.597
LILY ABSCONDED WITH HERSELF.

28:06.641 --> 28:08.991
FIRST TIME IN 30 YEARS
I DON'T KNOW WHERE SHE IS.

28:09.035 --> 28:11.733
I DIDN'T KNOW
WHERE ELSE TO GO.

28:11.777 --> 28:13.169
IT'S ALRIGHT.

28:13.213 --> 28:14.997
I'M SURE LILY WILL BE BACK.

28:15.041 --> 28:16.259
OH, YES.

28:16.303 --> 28:17.739
THOUGH I DON'T KNOW
ABOUT OLIVE,

28:17.783 --> 28:20.437
AND THEN, OF COURSE,
THERE'S CHARLOTTE.

28:20.481 --> 28:24.050
EVERYONE SEEMS TO BE LEAVING ME.
HOME IS MY HAVEN NOW.

28:24.093 --> 28:27.531
EVERYTHING THERE JUST REMINDS ME
OF EVERYTHING NOT THERE.

28:27.575 --> 28:28.619
CHUCK.

28:28.663 --> 28:30.621
I MEAN...CHARLOTTE.

28:30.665 --> 28:32.928
HER ROOM
IS HOW SHE LEFT IT --

28:32.972 --> 28:35.757
CLOTHES IN THE CLOSET,
HER BOOKS ON THE SHELVES...

28:35.801 --> 28:38.891
HER SPECIAL PILLOW
STILL AT THE HEAD OF THE BED.

28:38.934 --> 28:40.849
I DIDN'T KNOW
SHE HAD A SPECIAL PILLOW.

28:40.893 --> 28:42.546
IT WAS HER FATHER'S.

28:42.590 --> 28:44.287
I'M SURE IT'S TEEMING
WITH FUNGUS

28:44.331 --> 28:47.116
AND MICROSCOPIC BUGS THAT
FEED ON FLAKES OF HUMAN SKIN,

28:47.160 --> 28:49.336
BUT SHE WAS FOND OF IT.

28:49.379 --> 28:52.469
I KNOW YOU LOVED HAVING
CHARLOTTE SAFE AT HOME,

28:52.513 --> 28:55.298
SMILING ON THE OTHER SIDE
OF THE ROOM, BUT SHE'S GONE.

28:55.342 --> 28:57.692
SHE'S MOVED OUT.

28:57.736 --> 28:59.259
HMM?

28:59.302 --> 29:01.696
I MEAN, ON.
SHE'S MOVED ON.

29:01.740 --> 29:03.524
MAYBE IT'S TIME FOR YOU
TO MOVE ON

29:03.567 --> 29:07.049
AND...GET RID OF THAT PILLOW.

29:09.443 --> 29:12.881
Narrator:
AS THE PIE MAKER CONSIDERED
CHUCK'S WORLDLY BELONGINGS

29:12.925 --> 29:14.840
AND HOW VIVIAN
CLINGED TO THEM...

29:14.883 --> 29:16.189
[ BELL CHIMES ]

29:16.232 --> 29:17.930
...OLIVE WAS CLINGING
TO HER OWN.

29:17.973 --> 29:19.366
UH, EXCUSE ME.

29:19.409 --> 29:22.021
UH...
MOTHER SUPERIOR?

29:22.064 --> 29:23.805
HI.

29:23.849 --> 29:25.938
I HAVE BEEN HERE
FOR A DAY

29:25.981 --> 29:28.549
AND WAS TOLD THE PORTER
WOULD COME FOR MY THINGS.

29:28.592 --> 29:30.769
DO I NEED TO TELL HIM
WHAT ROOM I'M IN?

29:30.812 --> 29:32.161
THE POOR, SISTER.

29:32.205 --> 29:33.684
THE POOR WILL COME
FOR YOUR BELONGINGS --

29:33.728 --> 29:35.643
PART OF YOUR VOW
OF POVERTY.

29:35.686 --> 29:37.427
I THOUGHT THAT WAS
A TEMPORARY VOW

29:37.471 --> 29:39.255
SINCE I'M ONLY GONNA BE
A TEMPORARY NUN.

29:39.299 --> 29:44.043
UH, DON'T YOU HAVE SOME KIND
OF STORAGE FACILITY?

29:44.086 --> 29:47.133
THIS IS YOUR HOME
FOR AS LONG AS YOU'RE HERE,

29:47.176 --> 29:50.484
AND AS LONG AS YOU'RE HERE,
YOU WILL LIVE AS A NUN.

29:50.527 --> 29:52.312
BUT I LIKE MY BELONGINGS.

29:52.355 --> 29:54.401
THAT'S WHY THEY BELONG TO ME.
[ CHUCKLES ]

29:54.444 --> 29:58.361
I WANT TO BE POOR
IN OTHER WAYS.

29:58.405 --> 30:00.059
WE OFFER SANCTUARY,

30:00.102 --> 30:01.930
BUT IT DOESN'T COME
WITHOUT A PRICE.

30:01.974 --> 30:04.019
WORK HARD,
AND YOU WILL SEE RESULTS.

30:04.063 --> 30:05.542
COMMIT YOURSELF,

30:05.586 --> 30:08.110
AND YOU MAY EVEN FIND
THAT YOU WISH TO STAY.

30:08.154 --> 30:11.679
LIKE A GYM MEMBERSHIP.
I CAN CANCEL AT ANY TIME?

30:11.722 --> 30:13.507
GOD...

30:13.550 --> 30:16.510
IN HIS WISDOM,
HAS LED YOU HERE.

30:16.553 --> 30:18.512
TAKE REFUGE AND HIDE...

30:18.555 --> 30:20.862
your secret
from the world.

30:20.906 --> 30:22.864
AND ONCE YOUR BABY IS BORN,

30:22.908 --> 30:25.214
YOU CAN RETURN
TO THE OUTSIDE WORLD.

30:25.258 --> 30:28.174
OH. WHOA.
HOLD THAT PREGNANT PAUSE.

30:28.217 --> 30:30.350
[ CHUCKLES ]
I'M NOT WITH CHILD.

30:30.393 --> 30:32.352
UNLESS
IT'S IMMACULATE CONCEPTION

30:32.395 --> 30:34.397
OR I WORE
A STRANGE MAN'S UNDERWEAR.

30:34.441 --> 30:37.183
I JUST ASSUMED
BASED ON WHO BROUGHT YOU HERE.

30:37.226 --> 30:40.055
THIS IS WHERE LILY CAME
TO HAVE CHUCK?

30:40.099 --> 30:43.015
AH, HERE COME THE POOR.

30:43.058 --> 30:46.670
COME, HELP YOURSELVES.
HELP YOURSELVES.

30:46.714 --> 30:48.237
UM, NO, I --
LOOK AT THIS.

30:48.281 --> 30:50.283
-NO. I-I REALLY.
-LOOK AT THAT BEAUTIFUL CASE.

30:50.326 --> 30:52.633
I REALLY AM --
I'LL JUST TAKE THIS.

30:52.676 --> 30:54.374
HEY, LISTEN, POOR KID.
YOU GET --

30:57.159 --> 30:58.944
MY -- MY COUCH.

31:00.423 --> 31:01.903
UH, IS BETTY IN?

31:01.947 --> 31:04.036
SHE'S ON A CALL.
CAN I TAKE A MESSAGE?

31:04.079 --> 31:05.515
NED, WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE?

31:05.559 --> 31:08.388
FILING, FIELDING CALLS,
MAKING COFFEE.

31:08.431 --> 31:10.346
WHAT HAPPENED TO BETTY'S
OLD ASSISTANT, GIANCARLO?

31:10.390 --> 31:12.958
HE HAD TO, UM, SCOOT.

31:13.001 --> 31:15.569
Narrator: WHAT HAPPENED
TO GIANCARLO WAS THIS --

31:15.612 --> 31:17.266
AFTER EATING A SLICE OF PIE

31:17.310 --> 31:20.791
FROM WHAT HE BELIEVED WAS
A SECRET ADMIRER IN ACCOUNTING,

31:20.835 --> 31:24.230
GIANCARLO EXPERIENCED
WHAT COULD BEST BE DESCRIBED

31:24.273 --> 31:26.275
AS EXTREME INTESTINAL DISTRESS.

31:26.319 --> 31:27.842
[ GROANING ]

31:27.886 --> 31:29.626
YOU PRUNED HIS PIE?

31:29.670 --> 31:30.889
SENT HIM HOME
WITH THE SCOOTS.

31:30.932 --> 31:32.281
THEN I HID
IN HUMAN RESOURCES,

31:32.325 --> 31:34.066
WAITED FOR THEM TO CALL
HAPPY TIME TEMP AGENCY,

31:34.109 --> 31:35.763
THEN I CALLED
HAPPY TIME TEMP AGENCY,

31:35.806 --> 31:37.286
CANCELED THE ORDER,

31:37.330 --> 31:39.245
AND SHOWED UP WITH A SMILE
AND A PLEASANT ATTITUDE.

31:39.288 --> 31:41.551
I THINK THAT'S THE MOST
ROMANTIC THING I'VE EVER HEARD.

31:41.595 --> 31:42.944
[ BEEPING ]

31:42.988 --> 31:45.642
HE IS STALKING YOU.

31:45.686 --> 31:48.036
YOU DON'T THINK
I'M STALKING YOU?

31:48.080 --> 31:51.083
I'D BE A HYPOCRITE TO JUDGE YOU
FOR DOSING SOMEONE'S PIE.

31:51.126 --> 31:53.520
-WHY? ARE YOU STALKING ME?
-THAT DEPENDS.

31:53.563 --> 31:55.087
NOW THAT WE'RE LIVING
OUR NEW PARISIAN LIFESTYLE,

31:55.130 --> 31:57.306
DOES THAT MEAN I CAN'T BE CLOSE
WHEN DANGER'S AFOOT?

31:57.350 --> 31:58.960
I FEEL SAFER
NOW THAT YOU'RE HERE.

31:59.004 --> 32:01.658
THEN THIS ISN'T STALKING.

32:01.702 --> 32:05.227
[ Loudly ] IT'S JUST GOOD,
OLD-FASHIONED CHIVALRY.

32:05.271 --> 32:06.968
[ CHUCKLES ]

32:07.012 --> 32:08.665
[ DOOR OPENS ]

32:08.709 --> 32:10.189
WALK WITH ME.

32:10.232 --> 32:12.582
CANCEL ALL MY APPOINTMENTS.
I'M LEAVING EARLY.

32:12.626 --> 32:14.236
I'VE GOT ONE MORE THING
TO DO.

32:14.280 --> 32:16.673
HAVE MY CAR WAITING
FOR ME DOWNSTAIRS.

32:16.717 --> 32:21.461
Narrator:
WITH THE PIE MAKER SERVING
THE PERFECT DISTRACTION...

32:21.504 --> 32:27.946
CHUCK BEELINED
FOR THE STOLEN BEE KEY.

32:27.989 --> 32:30.426
[ BEE BUZZING ]

32:30.470 --> 32:33.690
SHE FOUND THE BEE KEY
EXACTLY WHERE BETTY BEE PUT IT.

32:33.734 --> 32:37.085
THEN SHE MADE AN EQUALLY
IMPORTANT DISCOVERY...

32:37.129 --> 32:39.261
OF A DIFFERENT KIND...

32:41.524 --> 32:44.614
...BEFORE SHE HERSELF
WAS DISCOVERED.

32:44.658 --> 32:47.574
[ BEES BUZZING ]

32:47.617 --> 32:48.662
AAH!

32:55.060 --> 32:56.322
[ GASPS ]

32:56.365 --> 32:58.150
CHUCK!

32:58.193 --> 33:00.152
[ BEES BUZZING ]

33:00.195 --> 33:02.110
I TOLD YOU
THIS WAS DANGEROUS.

33:02.154 --> 33:03.372
JUST BECAUSE
YOU'RE ALIVE AGAIN

33:03.416 --> 33:05.026
DOESN'T MEAN
YOU CAN'T BE DEAD AGAIN.

33:05.070 --> 33:06.680
THERE'S A REASON I DON'T LET
DIGBY PLAY IN TRAFFIC.

33:06.723 --> 33:09.509
I SUPPOSE
WE CAN TALK ABOUT THIS LATER.

33:12.991 --> 33:14.775
WHY ARE YOU POINT--
WHY IS SHE POINTING AT ME?

33:14.818 --> 33:17.473
WHY YOU -- WHY YOU
ROLLING HER TOWARD ME?!

33:17.517 --> 33:19.040
BECAUSE YOU'RE
IN FRONT OF THE DOOR!

33:19.084 --> 33:20.563
I -- OH.

33:20.607 --> 33:22.130
DON'T OFFEND THE BEES.
DON'T OFFEND THE BEES.

33:22.174 --> 33:23.871
DON'T OFFEND THE BEES.
DON'T OFFEND THE BEES.

33:23.914 --> 33:26.004
DON'T OFFEND THE BEES.
DON'T OFFEND THE BEES.

33:26.047 --> 33:28.397
DON'T OFFEND THE BEES.
DON'T OFFEND THE BEES.
DON'T OFFEND THE BEES.

33:28.441 --> 33:29.920
DON'T OFFEND THE BEES.
DON'T OFFEND THE BEES.

33:29.964 --> 33:31.183
DON'T OFFEND THE BEES.
DON'T OFFEND THE BEES.

33:35.100 --> 33:36.579
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]

33:36.623 --> 33:39.321
[ GRUNTS ]

33:39.365 --> 33:40.670
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU?

33:40.714 --> 33:42.455
Narrator:
WHAT HAPPENED WAS THIS --

33:42.498 --> 33:46.415
THE BEEMAN
WAS NOT COMPOSED OF BEES.

33:46.459 --> 33:48.939
THE DRONES NESTED
AROUND THEIR QUEEN,

33:48.983 --> 33:51.986
SAFE INSIDE THE BEEMAN'S MOUTH.

33:52.030 --> 33:53.161
AAH!

33:53.205 --> 33:54.945
WHEN HE SPAT THE QUEEN,

33:54.989 --> 33:57.644
SHE SIGNALED HER DRONES TO
ATTACK ANY PERCEIVED PREDATOR.

33:57.687 --> 34:00.168
-AAH!
-BUT UNLIKE KENTUCKY FITZ,

34:00.212 --> 34:03.302
CHUCK KEPT A COOL HEAD
AND AN OPEN MOUTH.

34:03.345 --> 34:06.914
SHE WAS NOT PERCEIVED
AS A PREDATOR, BUT A NEST.

34:08.916 --> 34:10.178
LOOK.

34:10.222 --> 34:11.788
THAT'S BETTY BEE
AS A LITTLE GIRL.

34:11.832 --> 34:14.617
WELL, EITHER SHE WAS AN
UNFORTUNATELY HAIRY CHILD, OR --

34:14.661 --> 34:17.055
BETTY BEE
IS THE TERRIFYING BEEMAN.

34:17.098 --> 34:18.491
WASN'T SHE WITH YOU?

34:18.534 --> 34:19.927
SHE DIDN'T GET OFF THE ELEVATOR
WITH ME.

34:19.970 --> 34:21.363
SHE MUST HAVE
COME BACK UP HERE

34:21.407 --> 34:24.105
TO WIGGETY-WHACK YOU
FOR BEING A SPY.

34:24.149 --> 34:26.020
LIKE SHE WIGGETY-WHACKED
KENTUCKY.

34:26.064 --> 34:29.719
WELL, MY WIGGETY WASN'T WHACKED.
AND I GOT THE BEE KEY.

34:29.763 --> 34:30.938
THAT'S A HOUSE KEY.

34:30.981 --> 34:32.722
I KNOW WHAT HOUSE
IT GOES TO.

34:32.766 --> 34:35.725
Narrator: AS CHUCK FOLLOWED
THE BEE KEY THAT WAS KEY,

34:35.769 --> 34:38.641
OLIVE SNOOK
FOLLOWED HER HOMESICK HEART

34:38.685 --> 34:39.990
TO THE CONFESSIONAL.

34:40.034 --> 34:41.514
FORGIVE ME, FATHER,

34:41.557 --> 34:43.690
FOR I AM GOING TO FILE
A POLICE REPORT

34:43.733 --> 34:46.084
ON ALL MY WORLDLY
POSSESSIONS.

34:46.127 --> 34:47.781
I KNOW IT'S GREEDY
AND WRATHFUL,

34:47.824 --> 34:50.218
BUT THERE'S BEEN
A MISCOMMUNICATION.

34:50.262 --> 34:52.264
AND SINCE
WE'RE DISCUSSING IT,

34:52.307 --> 34:55.484
I'M NOT REALLY
BELONGING HERE.

34:55.528 --> 34:58.835
AHA!
I KNEW YOU'D LAPSE.

34:58.879 --> 35:01.664
YOU! YOU HAVE SOME CRUST
COMING IN HERE LIKE THAT.

35:01.708 --> 35:03.318
HOW LONG
HAVE YOU BEEN LURKING?

35:03.362 --> 35:05.712
I'VE BEEN LURKING SINCE
YOU WALKED THROUGH THOSE GATES.

35:05.755 --> 35:08.280
I HAD TO MAKE SURE
YOU DIDN'T GET ANY IDEAS

35:08.323 --> 35:10.412
IN THAT NUBBIN OF YOURS
ABOUT LEAVING.

35:10.456 --> 35:11.761
OHH!

35:11.805 --> 35:13.198
IT'S YOUR FAULT
I'M HERE --

35:13.241 --> 35:16.026
YOU AND YOUR DAMN --
HAIL, MARY -- SECRETS!

35:16.070 --> 35:18.986
I SPENT SO MUCH TIME PRAYING,
I'VE RUN OUT OF THINGS TO SAY.

35:19.029 --> 35:21.597
I'M HAVING AWKWARD SILENCES
WITH GOD!

35:21.641 --> 35:23.164
I WANT TO GO HOME.

35:23.208 --> 35:24.905
WHERE'S HOME?

35:24.948 --> 35:27.386
[ SCOFFS ]
BACK TO SLINGING PIES?

35:27.429 --> 35:29.953
WHERE YOU SPEND
EVERY WAKING MINUTE PRAYING

35:29.997 --> 35:33.392
THAT THE MAN YOU WORSHIP WILL
SHOW YOU SOME SIGN OF HIS LOVE?

35:33.435 --> 35:35.524
YOU CAN DO THAT HERE...

35:35.568 --> 35:37.222
AND COMMISERATE.

35:37.265 --> 35:39.267
THESE NUNS
AREN'T MY PEOPLE.

35:39.311 --> 35:40.703
UNLESS YOU'RE TELLING ME
"FLIBBERTIGIBBET"

35:40.747 --> 35:42.879
IS A TITLE OF RESPECT.

35:42.923 --> 35:46.187
YOU KNOW THINGS ABOUT ME
NOBODY KNOWS.

35:46.231 --> 35:49.103
THIS PLACE KNOWS THINGS
ABOUT ME NOBODY KNOWS.

35:49.147 --> 35:51.105
LIKE THAT YOU HOLIDAYED HERE
30 YEARS AGO

35:51.149 --> 35:52.889
AND FOUND A BABY
IN A CABBAGE PATCH.

35:52.933 --> 35:56.415
AND BY "CABBAGE PATCH,"
I MEAN YOUR LADY PARTS.

35:56.458 --> 35:58.504
VIVIAN CAN NEVER KNOW
ABOUT THAT.

35:58.547 --> 36:00.027
SHE THOUGHT
I WAS IN PARIS,

36:00.070 --> 36:02.377
APPRENTICING
IN A WORLD-CLASS FROMAGERIE.

36:02.421 --> 36:05.467
WHY DON'T YOU
JUST TELL HER?

36:05.511 --> 36:10.429
CHARLOTTE'S FATHER, MY LOVER,
WAS VIVIAN'S FIANCE.

36:12.866 --> 36:16.174
YOU DID NOT JUST TELL ME
ANOTHER SECRET!

36:16.217 --> 36:17.218
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

36:17.262 --> 36:18.524
YOU'RE A HOME WRECKER, TOO!

36:18.567 --> 36:19.829
JIMINY CRISPY.

36:19.873 --> 36:21.440
DON'T "JIMINY CRISPY" ME.

36:21.483 --> 36:23.746
CHUCK THINKS HER MOTHER DIED
DURING CHILDBIRTH.

36:23.790 --> 36:25.879
I MEAN, ACCORDING TO VIVIAN,

36:25.922 --> 36:28.577
CHUCK -- CHARLOTTE THOUGHT HER
MOTHER DIED DURING CHILDBIRTH.

36:28.621 --> 36:30.536
WELL, IT DOESN'T MATTER
WHAT CHARLOTTE THOUGHT.

36:30.579 --> 36:32.668
SHE'S DEAD NOW.

36:32.712 --> 36:34.888
OH, LOOK AT YOU ALL PIOUS.

36:34.931 --> 36:36.368
[ SCOFFS ]

36:36.411 --> 36:38.283
YOU'D THINK YOU'D FIT RIGHT IN
IN A NUNNERY.

36:38.326 --> 36:39.849
HELL, IT MIGHT EVEN
DO YOU SOME GOOD.

36:39.893 --> 36:41.895
WHO ARE YOU --
THE GOOD-FOR-ME POLICE?

36:41.938 --> 36:43.462
OH, COME ON.

36:43.505 --> 36:47.161
THAT EPIC TANTY YOU PITCHED
BACK AT THE PIE HOLE --

36:47.205 --> 36:48.858
THAT WASN'T ALL MY DOING.

36:48.902 --> 36:51.948
I REALIZE I HAVE
SOME MAN ISSUES TO SORT OUT.

36:51.992 --> 36:53.863
SO, SORT THEM OUT.

36:53.907 --> 36:57.432
SORT THEM OUT HERE,
WHERE MEN WON'T BE AN ISSUE.

36:57.476 --> 37:01.784
STAY AS LONG AS YOU LIKE...
UNTIL YOUR HEAD IS CLEAR.

37:01.828 --> 37:05.701
Narrator:
BUT OLIVE FEARED LILY'S IDEA
OF "AS LONG AS YOU LIKE"

37:05.745 --> 37:09.227
WAS CONSIDERABLY LONGER
THAN HERS.

37:09.270 --> 37:11.838
39 MILES AWAY,
NORTH BY NORTHEAST,

37:11.881 --> 37:14.536
THE PRIVATE DETECTIVE,
THE PIE MAKER, AND CHUCK

37:14.580 --> 37:18.410
CLIMBED A WINDY ROAD TO
THE CHILDHOOD HOME OF BETTY BEE,

37:18.453 --> 37:21.151
A HOME
THAT WAS SUPPOSED TO BE VACANT.

37:21.195 --> 37:24.198
BUT THE HOME
WAS NOT VACANT AT ALL.

37:24.242 --> 37:27.157
[ BEES BUZZING ]

37:34.034 --> 37:36.123
Chuck: THAT COLONY COLLAPSE
WAS A HOAX.

37:36.166 --> 37:38.604
Ned: HER BEES DIDN'T DIE.
SHE STOLE THEM.

37:38.647 --> 37:39.953
DAMN.

37:39.996 --> 37:41.389
YOU KNOW,
SUDDENLY A CRAZY CAT LADY

37:41.433 --> 37:43.565
DON'T SEEM SO CRAZY NO MORE.

37:43.609 --> 37:45.001
[ BEE BUZZING ]

37:45.045 --> 37:47.265
SO KENTUCKY HELPED BETTY
STEAL BETTY'S BEES,

37:47.308 --> 37:49.005
THEY FAKE
A COLONY COLLAPSE,

37:49.049 --> 37:52.008
AND GET AWAY WITH CONSPIRACY,
SABOTAGE, AND GRAND THEFT.

37:52.052 --> 37:54.620
BUT WHY WOULD BETTY
WANT TO KILL KENTUCKY?

37:54.663 --> 37:56.404
MAYBE SHE DIDN'T KILL
KENTUCKY.

37:56.448 --> 37:58.450
WOOLSEY
HANDPICKED KENTUCKY

37:58.493 --> 37:59.842
TO BE THE NEW FACE
OF BETTY'S BEES,

37:59.886 --> 38:01.496
AND THEN SHE BETRAYED HIM.

38:01.540 --> 38:04.020
YEP, SHE SABOTAGED HIS COMPANY
AND STOLE HIS BEES.

38:04.064 --> 38:06.153
SHE PLAYED HIM
LIKE BOO-BOO THE FOOL.

38:06.196 --> 38:07.720
Betty:
BOO-BOO HAD IT COMING. EH!

38:10.984 --> 38:12.638
WOOLSEY TELLS ME
I'M TOO OLD

38:12.681 --> 38:15.641
AND SLAPS MY NAME
ON AN INFERIOR PRODUCT.

38:15.684 --> 38:18.470
DID YOU KNOW
THERE'S NOW 60% LESS HONEY

38:18.513 --> 38:21.777
IN ALL BETTY'S BEES' HONEY-BASED
PRODUCTS, INCLUDING HONEY?

38:21.821 --> 38:23.866
FINE. HE WANTS THE COMPANY,
HE CAN HAVE IT.

38:23.910 --> 38:26.434
BUT I'LL BE DAMNED
IF HE CAN HAVE MY BEES.

38:26.478 --> 38:27.914
HELLO, KITTY.

38:27.957 --> 38:30.090
AND YOU.
YOU'RE NOT A TEMP.

38:30.133 --> 38:31.831
WHO ARE YOU PEOPLE?

38:31.874 --> 38:34.007
WE'RE PRIVATE INVESTIGATORS
HIRED BY KENTUCKY'S HUSBAND

38:34.050 --> 38:35.574
TO FIND HER KILLER.

38:35.617 --> 38:37.924
THERE IS NO KILLER.
THAT'S WHAT THE POLICE TOLD ME.

38:37.967 --> 38:40.448
CAN'T PROSECUTE
A SWARM OF BEES FOR MURDER.

38:40.492 --> 38:42.276
YOU CAN PROSECUTE
WOOLSEY NICHOLLS.

38:42.320 --> 38:44.887
I LOVED KENTUCKY
LIKE A SISTER.

38:44.931 --> 38:46.976
BUT IF I TOLD THE POLICE
THAT WOOLSEY KILLED HER

38:47.020 --> 38:48.630
BECAUSE WE WERE SABOTAGING
HIS COMPANY,

38:48.674 --> 38:49.936
I WOULD GO TO JAIL
A LOT LONGER

38:49.979 --> 38:51.807
THAN WOOLSEY EVER WOULD
FOR MURDER.

38:51.851 --> 38:53.418
JAIL MIGHT BE
A SAFER PLACE FOR YOU.

38:53.461 --> 38:56.334
BETTY, I WAS ATTACKED IN
YOUR OFFICE BY A SWARM OF BEES,

38:56.377 --> 38:58.118
AND I THINK THOSE BEES
WERE MEANT FOR YOU.

38:58.161 --> 38:59.598
Ned: IF YOU LOVED KENTUCKY
LIKE A SISTER,

38:59.641 --> 39:01.121
YOU HAVE TO TELL THE POLICE
WHAT YOU KNOW.

39:01.164 --> 39:02.557
YOU CAN'T LET WOOLSEY
GET AWAY WITH MURDER.

39:02.601 --> 39:04.211
WOOLSEY IS
GONNA GET AWAY WITH MURDER.

39:04.254 --> 39:06.474
UNLESS YOU CAN PULL
HIS DNA OFF ONE OF THOSE BEES.

39:06.518 --> 39:08.346
TSK. OHH.

39:08.389 --> 39:09.912
OH.

39:11.174 --> 39:12.480
Emerson:
PLEASE DON'T GET UP.

39:12.524 --> 39:14.090
ALLOW ME
TO INTRODUCE MYSELF.

39:14.134 --> 39:15.788
MY NAME IS EMERSON COD.
I'M A PRIVATE INVESTIGATOR.

39:15.831 --> 39:17.050
I'D LIKE TO ASK YOU
A FEW QUESTIONS

39:17.093 --> 39:18.399
ABOUT THE MURDER
OF KENTUCKY FITZ.

39:18.443 --> 39:20.140
KENTUCKY WASN'T MURDERED.

39:20.183 --> 39:23.622
THE SWARM CHASED HER TO HER CAR
ALL THE WAY FROM THE COLONY.

39:23.665 --> 39:25.450
THAT SWARM FOLLOWED HER
ALL THE WAY FROM YOU,

39:25.493 --> 39:26.886
AND YOU TRIED TO KILL BETTY
THE SAME WAY,

39:26.929 --> 39:28.453
EXCEPT THAT WASN'T BETTY
IN HER OFFICE.

39:28.496 --> 39:30.629
THIS IS THE QUEEN-BEE CASE
THAT YOU SPAT AT ME

39:30.672 --> 39:32.282
WHEN YOU WERE COVERED
IN BEES.

39:32.326 --> 39:34.154
WE FOUND IT OUTSIDE
BETTY'S OFFICE UNDER A SWARM.

39:34.197 --> 39:35.851
AND IF WE TESTED IT
FOR SPITTLE,

39:35.895 --> 39:39.768
I'M SURE
WE'D FIND PLENTY OF YOURS.

39:39.812 --> 39:41.770
HA HA HA.

39:41.814 --> 39:44.730
WELL, I HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

39:44.773 --> 39:46.253
HMM.

39:46.296 --> 39:47.428
[ BEE BUZZING ]

39:47.472 --> 39:49.169
Narrator:
THE FACTS WERE THESE --

39:49.212 --> 39:53.347
WOOLSEY NICHOLLS WAS MADLY
IN LOVE WITH KENTUCKY FITZ.

39:53.391 --> 39:56.655
THE OPERATIVE WORD WAS "MADLY."

39:56.698 --> 39:58.874
BETTY BEE WAS A WITHERED HAG

39:58.918 --> 40:01.703
BY THE MERE FACT
THAT SHE WASN'T KENTUCKY.

40:01.747 --> 40:03.096
SHORTLY AFTER KENTUCKY

40:03.139 --> 40:05.272
GRATEFULLY ACCEPTED
WOOLSEY'S OFFER

40:05.315 --> 40:07.883
TO BECOME THE NEW FACE
OF BETTY'S BEES,

40:07.927 --> 40:11.060
HE DISCOVERED
HER GRATITUDE WAS INSINCERE

40:11.104 --> 40:14.107
AND HER INTENTION WAS SABOTAGE.

40:14.150 --> 40:18.067
INFECTED BEES WERE FOUND
IN KENTUCKY'S POSSESSION.

40:18.111 --> 40:22.898
SHE WAS SMUGGLING MITE-INFESTED
BEES INTO HIS NEW COLONY.

40:22.942 --> 40:26.032
BETRAYED AND BROKEN HEARTED,
BUT NOT SLOPPY,

40:26.075 --> 40:28.817
WOOLSEY DEALT WITH KENTUCKY
USING A MEANS

40:28.861 --> 40:32.342
THAT WOULD ALSO IMPLY
ACCIDENTAL DEATH.

40:32.386 --> 40:36.259
WOOLSEY NICHOLLS CONFESSED
TO THE MURDER OF KENTUCKY FITZ

40:36.303 --> 40:39.349
AND ATTEMPTED MURDER
OF BETTY BEE.

40:39.393 --> 40:41.700
HE NEVER KNEW
THE COLONY COLLAPSE WAS A HOAX

40:41.743 --> 40:45.399
OR THAT BETTY
HAD STOLEN BACK HER BEES.

40:45.443 --> 40:48.924
SINCE KENTUCKY FITZ
WAS LIKE A SISTER TO BETTY BEE,

40:48.968 --> 40:52.058
BETTY BEE WAS LIKE A SISTER
TO DUSTY FITZ

40:52.101 --> 40:54.321
AND MADE HIM HER NEW PARTNER.

40:54.364 --> 40:57.759
REALIZING THAT HIS COLONY
HAD NOT COLLAPSED,

40:57.803 --> 41:01.154
BUT HAD MERELY EXPANDED
INTO HIS-AND-HER SUITES,

41:01.197 --> 41:06.333
THE PIE MAKER LABORED TO MAKE
CHUCK'S SUITE FEEL LIKE HOME.

41:06.376 --> 41:08.291
ARE THOSE MY BOOKS?

41:11.425 --> 41:14.602
AND MY FURNITURE AND...

41:14.646 --> 41:17.344
[ GASPS ]

41:17.387 --> 41:19.694
MY SPECIAL PILLOW.

41:19.738 --> 41:22.392
HOW --

41:22.436 --> 41:24.220
WELCOME HOME.

41:24.264 --> 41:26.658
Narrator: AND SO THE PIE MAKER
HAD COME TO UNDERSTAND

41:26.701 --> 41:28.964
HOME DID NOT MEAN FOUR WALLS

41:29.008 --> 41:31.924
AND A DOOR
YOU NEVER WALK OUT OF.

41:31.967 --> 41:36.058
HOME WAS A FEELING
OF WHERE YOU BELONG.

41:36.102 --> 41:40.149
FOR EMERSON COD,
HOME WAS "LIL' GUM SHOE,"

41:40.193 --> 41:43.675
THE TALE OF A GIRL
WHOSE FATHER COULDN'T FIND HER,

41:43.718 --> 41:45.720
SO SHE HAD TO FIND HIM.

41:45.764 --> 41:48.854
MR. COD INSISTS
IT'S A WORK OF FICTION.

41:48.897 --> 41:50.290
BUT IF PUBLISHED,

41:50.333 --> 41:52.422
IT COULD SERVE
AS A HOW-TO MANUAL

41:52.466 --> 41:54.947
FOR AN AUDIENCE OF ONE.

41:54.990 --> 41:56.949
FOR OLIVE SNOOK,

41:56.992 --> 42:00.213
HOME WAS THE PLACE
SHE HOPED TO FIND HERSELF

42:00.256 --> 42:05.044
AND PERHAPS FIND NEW FRIENDS
WITH NOT SO MANY SECRETS.

42:05.087 --> 42:07.263
HIYA, PIGBY.
[ SNORTS ]

42:07.307 --> 42:12.573
FOR LONELY TOURIST
CHARLOTTE CHARLES, A.K.A. CHUCK,

42:12.617 --> 42:15.271
HOME WAS WHERE
THE PIE MAKER WAS.

42:15.315 --> 42:17.186
AND THIS HOME WAS A PLACE

42:17.230 --> 42:19.972
THE PIE MAKER'S FATHER,
WHO ABANDONED HIM,

42:20.015 --> 42:21.843
WOULD RETURN TO...

42:24.411 --> 42:28.328
EVEN IF THE PIE MAKER
NEVER KNEW HE WAS THERE.
